Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.93,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.48,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:40.06,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.65,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.65,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.57,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.99,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:55.45,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:03:00.33,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.80,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.26,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.60,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:21.81,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace in the great war against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:24.51,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was overwhelmed by sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.19,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,But now, we go back in time ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:34.50,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is the story of the brothers, Luffy and Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:51.58,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Again, we turn time back a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.14,0:03:55.75,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,To the night when the Celestial Dragon's ship\Ndocked in Goa Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.36,0:04:03.15,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,In a small village in a certain region of East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.44,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that guy with the huge face\Nwho was here this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.44,0:04:19.53,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!  I've never seen anything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:22.74,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Look!  His ship is huge too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.18,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred and eighty...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.18,0:04:27.24,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred and eighty one...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.24,0:04:29.95,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred and eighty two...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.75,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred and eighty three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.42,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Five hundred and eighty four...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.06,Main,Ivankov,0000,0000,0000,,Vyou're late, Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.92,Main,Ivankov,0000,0000,0000,,How long did vyou plan to keep vus waiting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:45.97,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.80,Main,Ivankov,0000,0000,0000,,Vyou... What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:50.60,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.96,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,You!  Quickly, bring a doctor!  This is an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.96,0:04:53.99,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:05:00.50,Main,Ivankov,0000,0000,0000,,Really... Where have vyou been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.28,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,I was watching the ceremony for the World Nobles. { def: should this be plural?  there's only one noble here }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:09.66,Main,Ivankov,0000,0000,0000,,How could vyou go there on vyour own,\Nwithout telling vme about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:14.12,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd been there, we'd have stood out too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.25,Main,Ivankov,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:23.67,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,We must grow stronger as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.13,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,How are our provisions?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.35,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,A dojo in the village offered us some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.82,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,Time to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.82,0:05:36.89,Main,Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to Baltigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.29,0:05:48.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Some months later, after the World Government's inspection of Goa Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.42,0:05:55.62,Main,Outcast,0000,0000,0000,,They've brought more trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:06:00.84,Main,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The people have settled into their old routines...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.84,Main,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The trash mountain is back, just like it was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.31,0:06:13.62,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:35.12,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?  You call this a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:42.57,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much force you put into it,\Nthere's no point if you can't hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:45.98,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, rubber really isn't suited for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.29,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!  Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:50.59,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  Are you trying to say that I'm wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:54.43,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You're just an anchor who's immune to bulletfire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.15,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the Gomu Gomu Fruit!\NSomeday, I'll make you cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:07:00.98,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I've thought up a technique more powerful than a pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.87,0:07:03.84,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.33,0:07:07.91,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,Your arm stretched a lot further than it did yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:11.45,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!  You're far too soft on Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.58,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I really have become strong!\NStronger than I was yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:16.36,Main,Ace & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sabo! {...So basically, they both had the same hallucination of the same (not) dead guy saying the exact same thing. How the hell does that work?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.64,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was such a kind older brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:39.77,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!  Would you rather {\i1}I{\i0} died instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:41.36,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:43.81,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,But that's basically what you meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:45.35,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:48.72,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo never punched me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.41,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!  Be a little nicer, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:52.12,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:00.87,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.06,0:08:13.72,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I've founded my own country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.25,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,A country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.23,0:08:19.45,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:22.98,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:27.36,Note,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(00,300)}Signs: Ace's Country, Luffy's Country
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.44,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.01,0:08:35.82,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna learn to survive on my own.  You guys can be Dadan's country.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:38.70,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna borrow your bath every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:06.85,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!  Help me out!  It's a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:09.95,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna survive on your own, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.03,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.71,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.45,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Dadan's country, is anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:43.56,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is injured!  Please, treat his wounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.16,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Magra!  Please, help Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.16,0:09:50.65,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Come in, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:07.00,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... This is no joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:11.26,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,If his wounds had been any worse,\Nhe could have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:16.51,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,The three of you always fought these wild beasts together as a team, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.22,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:27.26,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that I learned that fighting on your own\Ndoesn't prove that you're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.82,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.19,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Completely worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:38.28,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.62,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:42.78,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:54.59,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:58.77,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Makino-chan came all the way out here\Nto bring us some drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:02.51,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,How to greet people properly?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.36,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.36,0:11:06.38,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,What brought about this change of attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.38,0:11:08.90,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Luffy's brother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:15.59,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I'd like to meet Captain Red Hair, and\Nthank him for everything he did for my little brother. { def: tlc, changed line re manga }
