Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.13,0:11:46.05,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.18,Main,Ace & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.71,0:11:55.23,Main,Chef,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you damn kids!  Just pay the bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.70,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna win today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.56,Main,Ace & Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.72,Main,Ace,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we'll be having bear-stew for dinner!
