Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:58.31,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,That little brat was just hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:02.61,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right, I have a message to you from Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:07.36,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  Even now, after he's left, he's still complaining to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.92,0:16:10.40,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,He said, "Sorry for all the trouble, and thanks." { def: prolly should extend the end time on this }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.02,0:16:19.45,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot, he can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:23.36,Main,Bandit,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Boss, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.36,0:16:25.63,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not crying, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.22,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Only three more years for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:50.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... My aim was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.70,0:16:56.74,Main,Sabo,0000,0000,0000,,That was close, Luffy.  Why don't you just aim a little lower?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:19.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:23.17,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.33,0:17:33.03,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:35.00,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the newspapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.00,0:17:36.35,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:38.37,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:41.38,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!  Ace made a name for himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:43.69,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The picture shows him with his pirate ship and crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.69,0:17:47.32,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!  Ace is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.07,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna lose to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:01.22,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.22,0:18:03.73,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now.  Aren't you gonna see me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:05.31,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:07.56,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:14.84,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor and Makino know us, but we'd scare the other villagers if we came down from the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.91,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.76,0:18:18.36,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Just get going already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.22,0:18:22.12,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Well then, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.41,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.83,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't embarrass us... No need for thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.06,Main,Magra,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now... Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.02,0:18:35.01,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.87,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan!  I hate mountain bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:40.55,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.43,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,...but I like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:51.56,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say dumb stuff like that, and just get lost, damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.94,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, you guys are just...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:18:58.44,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:19:01.12,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:06.75,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Windmill Village, at the outskirts of the Goa Kingdom on Dawn Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:11.54,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you're going out to sea, then you should take my old fishing boat, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:14.09,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,You'll sink right away if you take that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.13,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,A rowing boat?  Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:20.55,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with this.  My journey begins right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.98,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:32.35,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!  I'm setting out to sea too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:37.89,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was first.  Ace was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.08,0:19:41.83,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the third to go, but I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:46.06,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Ace!  I'll catch up to you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:49.08,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Luffy?  Shouting and muttering to yourself like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.24,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Is it some sort of good luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.  It's a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:55.62,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:19:56.42,Main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.88,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.95,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,There he goes, mayor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.55,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:15.77,Main,Woop Slap,0000,0000,0000,,He's a disgrace to the village!  Becoming a pirate...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.93,0:20:23.40,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... It's a great day to set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.29,Main,Makino,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.94,0:20:44.22,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,So there you are, lord of the coastal waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.61,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,You picked the wrong opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.53,0:20:54.97,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Check out my attack, I've been practicing for the past ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.69,0:21:25.59,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Learned your lesson yet, damn fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:37.14,Main,Dogra,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible... He beat the lord of the coastal waters with one punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.74,0:21:41.15,Main,Dadan,0000,0000,0000,,He's grown strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:44.94,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,First, I've gotta gather a crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.19,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to have about ten people...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.33,0:21:50.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll need a pirate flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.76,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright... Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.66,0:21:58.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:02.46,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,the Pirate King!
